barroit.sh
==========

This repository is the profile page of barroit. It's hosted on barroit.sh and
licensed under GPL-3.0-or-later. Some files use their own license, like fonts
and artworks.

This site follows WCAG 2.1 AA a11y guidelines, but disables zoom via CSS. This
is intentional, as allowing zoom screws up layout consistency across devices.
That's not tolerated, so layout wins and zoom gets dropped.
